The container build sequence, install-flatpak.sh wrapper, install-desktop-mode.sh
template, and bootc switch flow originate from gameos-unlock. This playbook packages
that workflow as a guided walkthrough for AI coding agents (Claude Code, Codex,
Cursor, Aider, GitHub Copilot, Antigravity, etc.) — it does not modify or
redistribute the gameos-unlock code itself. Users are instructed to clone and run
gameos-unlock directly from its upstream repository.

